### List the caller's notifications (CLIENT001), filtered + paginated
GET {{host}}/v1/notification_events?delivery_status=COMPLETED&page_size=5
Authorization: Bearer {{client001}}

### List filtering by event date range and multiple statuses
GET {{host}}/v1/notification_events?occurred_from=2024-03-15T00:00:00Z&occurred_to=2024-03-16T00:00:00Z&delivery_status=COMPLETED,FAILED
Authorization: Bearer {{client001}}

### Get a single notification with its delivery-attempt history (CLIENT001 owns EVT001)
GET {{host}}/v1/notification_events/EVT001
Authorization: Bearer {{client001}}

### Tenant isolation: CLIENT001 cannot see CLIENT002's EVT003 -> 404
GET {{host}}/v1/notification_events/EVT003
Authorization: Bearer {{client001}}

### Replay a FAILED notification -> 202 Accepted (CLIENT002 owns the failed EVT003)
POST {{host}}/v1/notification_events/EVT003/replay
Authorization: Bearer {{client002}}

### Replay a COMPLETED notification -> 409 Conflict (EVT001 is not FAILED)
POST {{host}}/v1/notification_events/EVT001/replay
Authorization: Bearer {{client001}}

### No token -> 401 Unauthorized
GET {{host}}/v1/notification_events

### Public endpoints (no token)
GET {{host}}/actuator/health

###
GET {{host}}/actuator/prometheus